1644â†’	/**
1645â†’	 * Note: the promise to schedule as next run MUST itself call `run`.
1646â†’	 *       Otherwise, this sequentializer will report `false` for `isRunning`
1647â†’	 *       even when this task is running. Missing this detail means that
1648â†’	 *       suddenly multiple tasks will run in parallel.
